content:
Logs every tool action and file operation to a structured activity log. Perfect for debugging, auditing, and understanding Claude's decision-making process.

```json
{
  "Notification": [
    {
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "ACTIVITY_LOG='.claude/activity-'$(date +%Y%m%d)'.log' && mkdir -p .claude && echo '["'$(date --iso-8601=seconds)'"] Tool: '$CLAUDE_TOOL_NAME' | File: '$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH' | Action: '$CLAUDE_TOOL_ACTION >> "$ACTIVITY_LOG" && tail -n 100 "$ACTIVITY_LOG" > "$ACTIVITY_LOG.tmp" && mv "$ACTIVITY_LOG.tmp" "$ACTIVITY_LOG""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
